==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Limited
<hw>Lim"it*ed</hw> <pr>(l⟦icr⟧m"⟦icr⟧t*⟦ecr⟧d)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Confined within limits; narrow; circumscribed; restricted; <as>as,
our views of nature are very <ex>limited</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Limited company</b></col>, <cd>a company in which the
liability of each shareholder is limited by the number of shares he has
taken, so that he can not be called on to contribute beyond the amount
of his shares.</cd> <mark>[Eng.]</mark> <au>Mozley & W.</au></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Limitedly</ent>⟦br⟧
